{"type":null,"faqId":49484,"title":"通过便携式 WLAN 热点共享移动网络","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>通过将手机设置为 WLAN 热点，可以与其他设备共享移动网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"通过便携式 WLAN 热点共享移动网络\"XE \"开启 WLAN 热点\"XE \"设置 WLAN 热点\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189789\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”，然后切换到“全部设置”页签。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在“无线和网络”区域，点击“更多”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>点击“移动网络共享 &gt; 便携式 WLAN 热点”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 4  </span><span>点击热点开关，开启热点。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 5  </span><span>点击“配置 WLAN 热点”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 6  </span><span>设置 WLAN 热点名称、安全性以及访问密码，然后点击“保存”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189790\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>为了保护您的网络安全，建议将安全性设置为 WPA2 PSK。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5228","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294485000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":52,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}